		<method name="get_data" qualifiers="const">
			<return type="Array">
			</return>
			<description>
				Returns an array of shaped runs containing dictionaries with the following fields:
				[code]start[/code]: Run start offset.
				[code]end[/code]: Run end offset.
				[code]level[/code]: Embedding level and indicates the visual direction by its bit 0 (LTR is even, RTL is odd).
				[code]script[/code]: 4-byte script tag, can be re-interpreted as a four-character sequence.
				[code]width[/code]: Width.
				[code]ascent[/code]: Ascent.
				[code]descent[/code]: Descent.
				[code]break_type[/code]: 
				[code]clusters[/code]: An array of grapheme clusters containing dictionaries with the following fields:
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]start[/code]: Cluster start offset.
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]end[/code]: Cluster end offset.
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]advance[/code]:
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]repeat[/code]:
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]font[/code]:
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]font_outline[/code]:
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]flags[/code]:
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]glyphs[/code]: An array of glyphs containing dictionaries with the following fields:
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]index[/code]:
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]offset[/code]:
				&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;[code]advacne[/code]:
			</description>
		</method>
